<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「そうなんですか。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">とにかく、少々面倒でもバールのようなものがほ<sampling type="start" />しいわけです」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ですから、どういうものを捜しておられるのか、どうもよくわからなくて。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">バールじゃないんですね」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「違います」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「かなづちですか」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「違います」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「スパナとか」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「違います」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「スコップとかピッケルとか」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
